headline: Northern Trust (NTRS): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Northern Trust has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 10.9% to $144.88 per share while the index has gained 6.5%.
